---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Claim Guardians | Roof Damage Insurance Claim Florida" 
  description="Insurers downplay roof damage. Claim Guardians documents structural failure and forces your insurance company to cover a complete roof replacement in Florida."
>
  <!-- 1. Hero -->
  <header class="section-dark" style="padding-top:8rem; padding-bottom:8rem;">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb" class="mb-10 inline-flex">
        <ol class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-slate-400 font-medium bg-white/5 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-white/10">
          <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a></li>
          <li><span class="mx-2 text-slate-600">›</span></li>
          <li><a href="/services" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Services</a></li>
          <li><span class="mx-2 text-slate-600">›</span></li>
          <li class="text-white" aria-current="page">Roof Damage</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <span class="eyebrow" style="color:#00B5A6;">Property Damage — Roof &amp; Structure</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
          Claim Guardians Proves Your Roof Damage and Forces Full Replacement.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 mb-12 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          Insurance companies patch roofs when they should replace them. Claim Guardians documents structural failure and forces your insurer to pay for a proper, code-compliant replacement. You pay nothing upfront.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-5 mb-12">
          <a href="/free-claim-review" class="btn-accent px-10 py-5 text-lg min-h-[60px]">Get a Free Roof Damage Inspection</a>
          <a href="tel:5551234567" class="inline-flex justify-center items-center px-10 py-5 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-white/5 border-2 border-white/20 rounded-xl hover:bg-white/10 transition-all transform hover:-translate-y-1 min-h-[60px]">Call a Roof Expert Now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-10 gap-y-4 pt-6 border-t border-white/10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> FAPIA Licensed</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> No Recovery, No Fee</div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-300 font-semibold text-sm"><span class="text-[#00B5A6]">✓</span> FL Building Code Specialists</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- 2. Problem / Solution -->
  <section class="section-white">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">The Problem</span>
          <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">Insurers Offer Patches Instead of Replacements.</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            Insurance adjusters classify roof damage as "minor" to avoid paying for a full replacement. They ignore shingle granule loss, decking damage, and structural weakening that compromises your home's integrity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card-hover p-10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#082142] mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#002D51]/10 text-[#00808C]">✓</span>
            Claim Guardians Documents the Full Extent.
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-5">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4"><span class="text-[#00808C] mt-1">🏠</span><span class="text-lg font-medium text-[#082142]">We inspect decking, underlayment, flashing, and gutters.</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4"><span class="text-[#00808C] mt-1">📐</span><span class="text-lg font-medium text-[#082142]">We apply Florida building code upgrades to your claim (Code Upgrade Coverage).</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4"><span class="text-[#00808C] mt-1">⚖️</span><span class="text-lg font-medium text-[#082142]">We force your insurer to pay for a code-compliant full replacement.</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. Result Proof -->
  <section class="section-muted">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="eyebrow">Proven Results</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">We Turn Denied Claims into Full Replacements.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto card-testimonial">
        <span class="inline-flex px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 text-[#002D51] text-sm font-bold rounded-full mb-8 border border-blue-100">📍 Storm Damage Claim, Fort Lauderdale, FL.</span>
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-8 pb-8 border-b border-slate-100">
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-slate-500 font-medium text-sm uppercase">Insurance Initial Offer</span>
            <span class="text-red-400 line-through font-bold text-2xl">Claim Denied</span>
          </div>
          <div class="h-px bg-slate-100"></div>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:items-center gap-4">
            <span class="text-[#082142] font-bold text-sm uppercase">Claim Guardians Settlement</span>
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black text-4xl tracking-tighter">$65,000</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 -mx-10 -mb-10 p-10 rounded-b-3xl">
          <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Action Taken</h4>
          <p class="text-xl font-medium text-[#082142] leading-relaxed">We documented hidden structural roof damage the insurer's adjuster failed to report. The denied claim became a complete roof replacement settlement.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Final CTA -->
  <section class="gradient-accent-bar section-white text-center">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">No-Risk Consultation</span>
      <h2 class="section-heading mb-4">Does Your Florida Roof Show Storm Damage?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-500 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Our licensed adjusters inspect for free. We fight for a complete, code-compliant roof replacement.</p>
      <a href="/free-claim-review" class="btn-accent px-12 py-5 text-xl min-h-[64px]">Start Free Roof Claim Review →</a>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-4">Zero upfront cost. Ever.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="fixed bottom-0 left-0 right-0 p-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-md border-t border-slate-200 shadow-[0_-10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.1)] z-50 sm:hidden">
    <a href="tel:5551234567" class="btn-accent w-full text-lg">🚨 Emergency? Call Now</a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
